}}'''South Africa''' is an original [[Nations|country]] that was on BitLife in September 2018. Its default cities are the legislative capital, Cape Town, along with Durban, Johannesburg, and Soweto.

South Africa, alongside [[Morocco]] and [[Nigeria]] are the only countries where a capital is not a default city. South Africa has three capitals and only one of them is included. Cape Town (legislative) is included, but Pretoria (executive) and Bloemfontein (judicial) are not.

